<td><i>La Prisonnière</i></td>
<td>1923</td>
<td><i>The Captive</i><br />
<i>The Prisoner</i></td>
</tr>
<tr style="vertical-align: middle;">
<td>6</td>
<td><i>La Fugitive</i><br />
<i><a href="/wiki/Albertine_disparue" title="Albertine disparue">Albertine disparue</a></i></td>
<td>1925</td>
<td><i>The Fugitive</i><br />
<i>The Sweet Cheat Gone</i><br />
<i>Albertine Gone</i></td>
</tr>
<tr style="vertical-align: middle;">
<td>7</td>
<td><i>Le Temps retrouvé</i></td>
