<li><i>In Search of Lost Time</i>, Translated by <a href="/wiki/C._K._Scott-Moncrieff" title="C. K. Scott-Moncrieff" class="mw-redirect">C. K. Scott-Moncrieff</a>, Terence Kilmartin and Andreas Mayor (Vol. 7). Revised by D.J. Enright. London: Chatto and Windus, New York: The Modern Library, 1992. Based on the most recent definitive French edition (1987–89). <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0812969642" class="internal">ISBN 0-81296964-2</a>
